<br />
Despite Dmitry using 'fuck' a lot, I did read the original post, and all it did was <i>allow</i> the pupil to sue their former teacher. The original post points out they haven't won the lawsuit.<br />
<br />
[Edit: Btw, the simple solution to this is to allow the pupil to insert their own notes into their academic record, explaining their side of the story. So when someone reads it and sees 'despite what the teacher says, this suspension was for not eating my peas - see page 8 of the NYT on 23rd Jan 2007 for my teacher getting sacked over it' there'd be no need to tie up the lawcourts with stupid suits like this]
						</blockquote>
